	      <td class="cx1"></td>
	      <td class="cx2"><a class="point-up" href="?keys=GEWN-print-02-01-02-0076&amp;mode=TOC" title="The Capitulation of Fort Necessity, 3 July 1754"></a></td>
	      <td class="cx3"></td>
	    </tr>
          <tr class="R2">
